{"tid":508283,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［絲打入］因為口技太好 男朋友成日懶得屌我 可以點？","createTime":"2017-12-24T06:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T13:42:12.000Z","uid":129221,"like":4,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a7450cb49f258791b540e2805d1d0c5375bbf9f9","tid":508283,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"佢會搵籍口話啲dom貴 咁佢負責交租係唔多錢既 咁唔通要我自己買套比佢屌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n含同屌既比例大概係三比一...但佢好似無考慮過我既需要 佢話含唔洗搞咁多 我含得佢又爽 如果搞野 搞完又要沖涼 而家冬天更加唔肯... <br />\n同埋佢太長 好多時都比佢插到喉嚨痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇絲打教我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一諗起就眼濕濕 喊住出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0838c7ae2550590e70a31912cab354bac082fe2","tid":508283,"uid":3764,"like":73,"dislike":2,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:01:30.000Z","msg":"叫佢幫你含返<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a506757ea81e8510fb40867fcaa8050317f93d19","tid":508283,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db212a49088452a10be073e749c11e89eb4117fa","tid":508283,"uid":69661,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"你屌番佢"},{"pid":"c9f757b5e6c8411f538696c6f3b79c1c67e8ad28","tid":508283,"uid":145744,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:02:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d350c19180bd7ef87c2adad829b24cf612e0a1b0","tid":508283,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"其實佢對我好好 知我屋企有問題即刻出錢租出黎一齊住 但係某方面就有啲自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然佢工作忙 放工好攰"},{"pid":"fc692b0d118de4f6c9e3717a22d014bafd30693d","tid":508